{"tid":1891980,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"【黑警中肺炎】三萬個病人 [原歌:十六號愛人]","createTime":"2020-02-22T08:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T16:02:20.000Z","uid":302130,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"548bab68819488d2989da13e49c3bf94a79fd641","tid":1891980,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"手足支持 黑警沒法醫<br />\n全城都喜慶 全靠武漢肺炎<br />\n才可把攬炒加碼威過實戰<br />\n當佢上次去食飯時 只希望個個有事<br />\n防暴有病患祝福佢無人醫<br />\n<br />\n想起當時 蠢也沒法子<br />\n毅進仔可以 碟燒鵝分開夾沒有意思<br />\n原來武肺最愛佢不過暫時<br />\n人數每隔兩日都多過上次<br />\n一變四 四變十二<br />\n來到這禮拜更加happy<br />\n<br />\n齊慶 佢老母冚家中武漢肺炎<br />\n隨便吐兩下口水都比以往更作討厭<br />\n偶爾我亦願佢人傳人 能上去救災別再擰埋面<br />\n佢似乎未確診  一個個廢到唔係人<br />\n還稱要上去救災 盡量集結給黨的吻<br />\n<br />\n沒有外遊 都變到白晒<br />\n當你要愛國變強大 要中嘅就快"},{"pid":"beb0a607de29a2eca678b4ede2ca2c97da7bd532","tid":1891980,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7c8bb33b69c51bc08fefd836fab8f2d95b9c2c","tid":1891980,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"救高人幫手睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e863f248693475016efe48ce8fb5f3ddc237ed","tid":1891980,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0a13c9c6e05c362aad25ea13b254ae829c3626","tid":1891980,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:35:31.000Z","msg":"中規中矩，留名"},{"pid":"81df78ef1decb8ae4d1f7d921c930322e0d83815","tid":1891980,"uid":302130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T08:36:22.000Z","msg":"各位大大俾啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 